`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

Clans are groups of people who have similar dreams, goals, motives etc. who
have banded together to become more powerful.  Prophecy's current clans can be
found by typing '`&clan list``'.  More information on a particular clan might
be found by typing '`&help <clan_name>``' from "clan list" or by talking to one
of the clan members. ``

